29_liverofsulfur.name: Copper Dragon (Liver of Sulfur)
29_liverofsulfur.description: This egg gleams with a reddish shine
29_liverofsulfur.note: This dragon has a total of 4 different variant sets, 3 CB and 1 bred. variant colors shown by eggs. This variant, the Liver of Sulfur, can be obtained in the Desert and Volcano. The last variant, Pennybright, must be bred by crossing a Copper with a Lightning alligned dragon. Any other breeding attempt will usually result in the Copper matching the mother's habitat (or Father's if the Mother is not caveborn)

32_1.name: Undead Western
32_1.note:
There's one of these for each dragon body type and stage.
Can only be produced by using the revive option on a dead dragon. Chance of revival is higher at Night, even higher on the 31st of a month, and the highest possible on Halloween's breeding week.
